"A.P.241/11/8": "Sniff-sniff... Sniff-sniff..."
"Cut it out already, Aurora. I thought you were supposed to have been the goddess of beauty."
"I can't help it, something seems off. Besides, do I look like the kind of girl who would cling to her past?"
"...That's rich, coming from you."
"What are you two doing? You look kind of suspicious."
"Ms. Former Goddess of Beauty here said she felt something, and started acting all weird. You have any idea what it could be?"
"Do I have any idea...?"
"Hm? Ah, I got it! It's coming from you, <%me>! You've got this weird smell coming from you!"
"From <%me>? I'm not detecting anything on their person that could be causing a weird smell..."
"How close did you check? There's deeefinitely something off. A lady's intuition is never wrong."
"...So it's just a hunch? It's not any kind of concrete sensation?"
"Wellll... It feels nostalgic, and scary?"
"Huh? Those aren't smells at all."
"Shut up, Yu! You asked me to describe it so I did!"
"If it's something you can sense like that, then what were you running around with your nose in the air for? You looked ridiculous."
"Th-That was... It increased the range of my perception!"
"I should have guessed the Goddess of Beauty would be an expert on scent."
"You went there! You really went there! I can't believe you'd say something so dumb!"
"What could Aurora find nostalgic and scary...?"
"Could it be the Photoners?"
"Could it be Dark Falz?"
"That's one possibility, but we can't rule out the possibility of it being related to Dark Falz, either."
"Yeah, it could be that. Since it's Aurora, it's possible that it's connected to the Photoners as well."
"Aurora's body is just an accumulation of Photons in her image... So it's possible it's related to the other world."
